The paper deals with the problem of finding maximal independent sets in hypergraphs, which is a fundamental problem in the theory of parallel computing. This problem is closely related to topics such as data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), distributed computing (cs.DC), and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
